snippet.textDisplay: There was actually extensive testing done by Coca Cola to see which tastes better: original coke, Diet Coke, or Pepsi. Diet Coke came first, Pepsi second, and original coke third. So they based the new coke formula off the Diet Coke formula and it tested better than all of them. So most other places in the world have new coke, but America has original coke because we all threw a fit because original coke has a nostalgia factor. We literally picked the worst tasting cola because we were nostalgia. 😬 also, can confirm, new coke is better than Pepsi and original coke, hands down.
